  "description": [
    "EwellsSt Paul Church Notes CLAYTON On Sunday July 8 at the morn ing worship at 10 the Rev Rob ert S Womer of Newark New Jersey will be the guest speaker Ruth Ann Sylvester and Frank Cole Whalen were united in Holy Matrimony by the minister the Rev W H Hitchens on Saturday evening June 30 at 8 oclock in the churchThe sympathy of the Church is extended to the family of Mrs Edith Mills member of this Communion who entered the Greater Ufe on June 24The Devotional Reading for Today Put not your trust in princes nor in the son of man in whom there m no help His breath go forth he returns to the earth in that very day his thoughts perish Paalms 14634 ItemsMr and Mrs Albert Bacon from Philadelphia were the Wednesday guests of Mr and Mrs Roscoe Wharton Clayton AvenueMr and Mrs Elmer T Gove have moved from the J B Thompson property on Highland Avenue to their new home local d on Glenwood Avenue A scant few local residents were observed attending the Democratic Citizens for Hoey meeting at the Clayton _ J Fire House last Saturday even ingCharles R Pryor local farmer"
